data.title: Taking care of 5,000+ users?
data.text:
TGIF, Spice-friends!

Do any of you happen to work for companies that have 5,000 or more users that you help manage IT for? Would love to ask some quick questions about how you use this community, social media, etc.

Comment below or PM me and we can get the convo going!

Thanks, all!

Kim@SOPHOS
